room_title: Escape room "The Execution" by Xcape The Quandary in Tulsa
room_description: You have spent weeks going over the evidence in your uncle’s case. You are now down to the last 60 minutes of your uncle’s life. Its 11pm and you are still hoping to find that one thing that can save him! You know he is innocent and you have to find a way to prove it! To see an innocent man executed will haunt you for the rest of your life. Failing him is not an option!
